Editors note: As FreePBX have told us and thus following the same train of thought, this is intended functionality and at best informational.Sifting For GoldBriefly perusing logs from our Attacker Eye FreePBX sensor, and filtering out the absolute junk created by AI-generated emoji-drenched ‘PoCs’, we found something interesting:POST /admin/ajax.php HTTP/1.1
Host: {{Hostname}}
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded
